body_html:
I found a preliminary workaround. When the compilation fails, to generate some of the missing objects I had to add the following include directives:

-I/home/root/.cache/bazel/_bazel_turing/508b67e7022bdc82335b30f64f498c49/tensorflow/external/eigen_archive/eigen-eigen-ed4c9730b545/ -I/home/root/.cache/bazel/_bazel_turing/508b67e7022bdc82335b30f64f498c49/tensorflow/external/eigen_archive/

Apparently those are missing. Can you comment about it?
